#Skill:  Archery [9579]
#
Usage:  USE @@@@
Time:   seven days

Learning @@@@ gives the noble a +50 missile attack rating.

Use of @@@@ will cause the noble to spend time and effort
practicing archery further.  Every seven-day use will
increase the noble's missile rating by one point.

Knowledge of Archery also allows the noble to train archers and
elite archers, via the TRAIN order.
